title: Episode 274: Put Yo Hood Up! (Feat. Chanel West Coast)
itunes:title: Episode 274: Put Yo Hood Up! (Feat. Chanel West Coast)
description:
Rapper/singer/TV Personality Chanel West Coast is here this week to promote her new album “America’s Sweetheart.” Chanel opens up about why she feels like she wasn’t taken seriously as a rapper, the evolution of her musical sound, her biggest misconceptions, and much more. The ladies even discuss if they’d be down for an hour long orgasm. Enjoy!
